import { AppBar, Badge, Grid, IconButton, InputBase, Toolbar } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function Header() {
    return (
            <AppBar position="static">
                <Toolbar>
                    <Grid container>
                        <Grid item sm={6} style={{ border:'1px solid #fff' }}>
                            <InputBase />
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item sm={6} style={{ border:'1px solid #000' }}>
                            <IconButton>
                                <Badge></Badge>
                            </IconButton>
                        </Grid>
                     </Grid>
                </Toolbar>
            </AppBar>
    )
}
